        "timestamp": 1761590144
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I would put it differently: your code gets reviewed much faster if you clean it up <em>before</em> making a PR. (And, of course, if you learn something during review, you apply it to the remaining code in your project also.)</p>",
        "id": 547366548,
        "sender_full_name": "Michael Rothgang",
        "timestamp": 1761597181
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I would like your result to get in, but my review time is also limited. Can we make a deal? You do your very best to clean up your code, by hand, using all the Lean knowledge you know, and then I'll take a look promptly at your first PR?</p>",
